ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this class. We covered a broad range of topics and the workload was very reasonable.
A course about cognitive development covering readings from various disciplines related to psychology.I would definitely recommand it.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I now have a better understanding of infant topics and research in the area.

I learned in this course how other areas are connected to psychology. And that I should not be afraid to look through the literature of other fields of science and should remain open and not restrict my interest just in one field.This experience will help me in my future research projects.
